{"id":47621111200,"slug":"it-is-not-advisable-to-drive-the-rickshaw-after","type":"text","date":"2013-04-10 14:26:32 GMT","timestamp":1365603992,"format":"html","tags":[],"highlighted":[],"note_count":0,"title":null,"body":"<p>It is not advisable to drive the rickshaw after dark. Or in cities. Or on roads under construction restricted to a single lane with potholes so big they can roll the vehicle. Especially don&rsquo;t do all these things during rush hour while rolling into a town looking for a place to stay with no plan at all.</p>"}